  "short_description": "Test your skills in this immersive VR space opera by Star 1 Studio. Utilize lightning sabers to strike down hordes of bionic extraterrestrials. Fight your way to the heart of the planet to defeat Attackian Leader RahKah. Unlock 10 missions, 10 alien landscapes, 8 saber colors, and a secret weapon.",
