  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to MASS, the Mega Asteroid Suppression Service, Agent. Your job is to protect this space station with your lightning sabers against Asteroids and Aliens. Are you ready?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test Your Skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 10 missions with increasing difficulty, can you complete them all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 1V1 mode against an elite alien drone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Use the local leader-board to compete with friends and family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn Goudas And Unlock Items!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock cosmetic upgrades for your sabers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Discover new alien landscapes and add them to your collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Uncover a secret weapon befitting an elite MASS agent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive VR Environments!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 3d sound to help you pinpoint the location of enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unique alien landscapes with custom music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and More!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play in endless mode, adjust the angle and speed to fit your skill level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fight your way to the top of the global leader-board.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Animated credits scene featuring a dance battle between the Attackians and MASS.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Access the Alien Dex to examine the Attackians up close.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good Luck, Agent.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to MASS, the Mega Asteroid Suppression Service, Agent. Your job is to protect this space station with your lightning sabers against Asteroids and Aliens. Are you ready?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test Your Skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 10 missions with increasing difficulty, can you complete them all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 1V1 mode against an elite alien drone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Use the local leader-board to compete with friends and family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn Goudas And Unlock Items!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock cosmetic upgrades for your sabers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Discover new alien landscapes and add them to your collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Uncover a secret weapon befitting an elite MASS agent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive VR Environments!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 3d sound to help you pinpoint the location of enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unique alien landscapes with custom music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and More!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play in endless mode, adjust the angle and speed to fit your skill level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fight your way to the top of the global leader-board.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Animated credits scene featuring a dance battle between the Attackians and MASS.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Access the Alien Dex to examine the Attackians up close.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good Luck, Agent.</p>",
